# {{ project_name }}

## Project Structure

This is a pnpm monorepo managed with Turborepo.

- `apps/` — Application packages
- `packages/` — Shared libraries and configuration

## Commands

- `pnpm dev` — Start all apps in development mode
- `pnpm build` — Build all packages
- `pnpm test` — Run all tests
- `pnpm lint` — Lint with Biome
- `pnpm typecheck` — TypeScript type checking
- `pnpm db:push` — Push Prisma schema to database
- `pnpm db:studio` — Open Prisma Studio

## Development

1. `docker compose up -d` — Start Postgres
2. `pnpm install` — Install dependencies
3. `pnpm db:push` — Push database schema
4. `pnpm dev` — Start development servers

## Conventions

- Strict TypeScript (`strict: true`)
- Biome for linting and formatting (not ESLint/Prettier)
- All packages use workspace protocol (`workspace:*`)
- Every app and package has at least one test
